    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-06-12T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-06-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="1264"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1264">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/7910.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Schmutz</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Aguascalientes</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-06-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 12, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to report that I left to [go to]
                    the city of Zacatecas on the 10th instant to inquire into the conditions of the
                    American and other foreign residents in that city.* * *</p>
                <p>Pánfilo Natera levied a forced loan on the commercial and financial houses
                    amounting to a total of $110,000.00 Mexican Cy. and the following are a few of
                    the largest contributors: <table cols="2" rows="7">
                        <row>
                            <cell>The National Bank of Mexico</cell>
                            <cell role="num">$9,000.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Bank of Zacatecas</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5,000.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>El Bote Mining Company (English)</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5,000.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Magistral Mine Company (American)</cell>
                            <cell role="num">4,000.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Parroquia</cell>
                            <cell role="num">2,000.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Fresnillo Mining Company (American)</cell>
                            <cell role="num">800.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Gualterio C. Palmer (English)</cell>
                            <cell role="num">500.00</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>I have [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gaston Schmutz</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
